# Keep build context small. Mirrors .gitignore plus a few container-specific exclusions.

## .NET
**/bin/
**/obj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
.idea/
*.swp

## Local dev artefacts
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
artifacts/
publish/
out/

## Tests
TestResults/
coverage/
*.coverage

## Secrets — never bake these into images
.env
.env.local
deploy/.env
secrets/
*.pfx
*.key

## Local docker state from deploy/docker-compose.yml
deploy/data/

## VCS metadata (not needed by builds)
.git/
.github/

## global.json pins SDK 10.0.100 for the plugin's net10 build, but server projects
## target net8.0 and run in mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/sdk:8.0 which doesn't have 10 SDK.
## Excluding it lets the container use whichever SDK ships in the base image.
global.json

## Editor / OS junk
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
